Class Entities

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.Entities
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MovableEntities

    public abstract class Entities
extends java.lang.Object
implements Entity
    An abstract class that is the super for all entities. This class includes functionality shared by all other entities
